ss it to my other forwards to make an easy goal. He well unfortuantely be switched to goalie as soon as the other teams catch up to us.<br>(LD)  - Naida is a great Defender with the high attack and pass stats, but what makes her stick out is her amazing speed. My only fret is her loser Endurance.<br>(RD) - Shaami, she has a high attack, high endurance, high speed, high shot. Shes like my replacement for wedge except her block is nothing compared to wedges though.<br>(GL) - I couldnt really get rid of keepa and find another goalie so im just going to wait until Keepa's Catch stat stops climbing to replace him.<br>(Bench 1) - Blappa is currently my benched defender, great everything but im just saving him for when my team needs to rid of Keepa.<br>(Bench 2) - Vilucha is another benched defender, I dont know why i picked her up, but her shot rating is high so i guess its ok, ill probably replace her with an Al Bhed.<br><br>Blitzball in general is pretty cool, its easily my favorite mini game which even beats out  FF7's Golden Saucer game &quot;G-Bike&quot; and FF8 and FF9's card games. I probably going to buy a gamecube for more FF games but Dance Dance Revolution will probably drain my money before I hit that $130.00 <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#aaaaaa><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon3.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub25.ezboard.com/uspikescafe.showPublicProfile?language=EN>SpikesCafe</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.spikescafe.com/shell.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Gamera <img src=http://contest.polykarbon.com/badge1.gif></span><br> <font color=#336699>(7/27/02 7:00:00 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub25.ezboard.com/fpolykarbonbbsfrm31.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=84.topic&index=1>Reply</a>    <br>ezSupporter